Slawinski, Wojciech Andrzej; Sjåstad, Anja Olafsen & Fjellvåg, Helmer (2016). Stacking Faults and Polytypes for Layered Double Hydroxides: What Can We Learn from Simulated and Experimental X-ray Powder Diffraction Data?. Inorganic Chemistry.  ISSN 0020-1669.  55(24), s 12881- 12889 . doi: 10.1021/acs.inorgchem.6b02247